'BRUN IIGS COLOR' TO INSTALLAMPERSAND ROUTINES THAT CAN BE USEDON THE APPLE IIGS. &Kn - CHANGE BACKGROUND COLOR TO n &Bn - CHANGE BORDER COLOR TO n &Tn - CHANGE TEXT COLOR TO nn MUST EVALUATE TO A NUMBER BETWEEN0 AND 15; INCLUSIVE.THE CHANGES ARE NOT PERMANENT; THATIS; THEY DO NOT CHANGE THE GSCONTROL PANEL SETTINGS.